# Deployment Skill

> **Trigger**: Use this skill when asked to deploy, release, ship, or promote the application to any environment. Also use when asked about rollback procedures.

## Environments

| Environment | URL | Branch | Auto-deploy |
|------------|-----|--------|-------------|
| Development | {{DEV_URL}} | `{{DEV_BRANCH}}` | {{DEV_AUTO_DEPLOY}} |
| Staging | {{STAGING_URL}} | `{{STAGING_BRANCH}}` | {{STAGING_AUTO_DEPLOY}} |
| Production | {{PROD_URL}} | `{{PROD_BRANCH}}` | {{PROD_AUTO_DEPLOY}} |

## Pre-Deployment Checklist

1. All tests pass: `{{CMD_TEST}}`
2. No type errors: `{{CMD_TYPECHECK}}`
3. No lint errors: `{{CMD_LINT}}`
4. Build succeeds: `{{CMD_BUILD}}`
5. {{EXTRA_PRE_DEPLOY_CHECK}}
